message.body: Rise and shine
I'll rise, but I don't know about the shine part :) Good morning to you too!
How was your bachelorette partiesV
I had bachelorette parties?
You had parties with your friends this weekend?

Things actually got moved around. And luckily it did because there was too many things happening this week. My friend decided to move her birthday stuff next weekend so that she could go visit her boyfriend in D.C. I ended up heading out with another friend because I told her I was going to do something with her, and it ended up being this weekend. While i had to babysit in the meantime. How were the seminars?
Wow you're such a social butterfly
The seminar was very educational in terms ofleadership
I don't think I am, I think it just happens that multiple things just falls on the same weekends for me sometimes.
Gotcha. What are you doing today?
Oh that's good, sounds like you enjoyed it.
I have to run home for a bit to change and come back to my sister's to relieve Tam of babysitting duties so she can leave. I don't know how parents do this, it's exhausting! How's your Sunday going?
Yeah we start to appreciate parents when we realize how hard it is. I'm heading to gym and then maybe look at some clothing stores. Finally a warmer day
Just walnut street. Wanna join me later?
It is?! Aw I want I take a walk. I miss fresh air! Clothes shopping huh? Headed to the mall?
I can't :( I'm going to be alone with the twins later. Unless you want to go shopping with toddlers hahah!
No I'm good thanks
Hahah I thought as much!
If I gave you $100,000 to jump out of an airplane without a parachute. Would you do it?
No.
What if I told you the plane was on the ground? :)
Is the ground also quicksand?
Or an island in the middle of the ocean with no ways to get off?
The plane is as small as you want. The point of the exercise is to get the complete facts lol.
It's ok. I failed too.
What a sneaky sneaky exercise.
I know
